  <thing id="cAMMstStr1" name="Mists Stride 1/day" description="At 5th level, an Anchorite of the Mists can use {i}dimension door{/i} once per day, as a sorcerer with a level equal to the character&#146;s primary divine spellcasting level plus his Anchorite of the Mists level. At 7th level, he can use this ability twice per day, and at 9th level he can use it three times per day." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Use {i}dimension door{/i} as a sorcerer 1/day.">
