  <thing id="cAMTruMist" name="Truce of the Mists" description="At 7th level, an Anchorite of the Mists is protected from creatures with the Mists descriptor as long as he takes no actions against them. Mists creatures may not attack the Anchorite of the Mists or target him with spells or spell-like or supernatural abilities, so long as the character refrains from attacking them in kind. This ability is similar to the {i}sanctuary{/i} spell, save that the creatures are not allowed a Will save to attack normally, and the effect&#146;s duration is permanent until broken by the character." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain the benefits of {i}sanctuary{/i} against creatures of the Mists.">
