  <thing id="cKnShadow" name="Knight of the Shadows" description="Few secret societies in the Land of Mists are as steeped in legend and contradiction as the Circle. Its members, the Knights of the Shadows, are men and women of supreme virtue and mystery. Gathering annually in the cursed domain of Avonleigh, the Knights go fourth in search of the wicked, pledge to selflessly protect the innocent. Yet theirs is not a life of accolades and glory. As their appellation implies, the Knights walk in darkness, emerging wherever they are needed and vanishing just as suddenly. Those who are pure of heart seem to be drawn to them, yet the Knights cloak themselves in secrecy, lest the masters of evil in the Realms of Dread seek them out and destroy them utterly. Theirs is a lonely way, promising endless hardship and no reward but the gratification of good deeds done. It is not a path to be tread lightly.\n\nMost Knights of the Shadows are fighters, rangers, or paladins, but the Circle will accept any soul who proves his prowess and willingness to sacrifice his own life for good. Clerics, rogues, and even a barbarian have all been initiated into the Knights at one point.\n\n{b}Special Requirement{/b}: The character must be initiated into the Circle by other Knights of the Shadows." compset="ClassLevel" maxlimit="10">
    <tag group="ClassType" tag="Prestige"/>
    <bootstrap thing="cHelpKoS"></bootstrap>
    <link linkage="helper" thing="cHelpKoS"/>
    <exprreq message="Base Attack Bonus +6 required."><![CDATA[child[Attack].field[tAtkBase].value >= 6]]></exprreq>
    <exprreq message="Courage required."><![CDATA[#hasfeat[fRvnCourag] <> 0]]></exprreq>
    <exprreq message="Dead Man Walking required."><![CDATA[#hasfeat[fRvnDMWalk] <> 0]]></exprreq>
    <exprreq message="Gather Information 4 ranks required."><![CDATA[#skillranks[kGatherInf] >= 4]]></exprreq>
    <exprreq message="Knowledge (local) 4 ranks required."><![CDATA[#skillranks[kKnowLocal] >= 4]]></exprreq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="sKotS1001" name="Bless" description="{i}Bless{/i} fills your allies {b}(all allies within a 50-ft. burst, centered on the caster){/b} with courage. Each ally gains a +1 morale bonus on attack rolls and on saving throws against fear effects.\n\n{i}Bless{/i} counters and dispels {i}bane{/i}." compset="Spell" summary="Allies gain +1 on attack rolls and +1 on saves against fear.">
