  <thing id="sKotS2005" name="Fog Cloud" description="A bank of fog billows out from the point you designate {b}(a 20 ft. radius, 20 ft. high spread){/b}. The fog obscures all sight, including darkvision, beyond 5 feet. A creature within 5 feet has concealment (attacks have a 20% miss chance). Creatures farther away have total concealment (50% miss chance, and the attacker can&#146;t use sight to locate the target).\n\nA moderate wind (11+ mph) disperses the fog in 4 rounds; a strong wind (21+ mph) disperses the fog in 1 round.\n\nThe spell does not function underwater." compset="Spell" summary="Fog obscures vision.">
