  <thing id="sKotS4001" name="Death Ward" description="The subject is immune to all death spells, magical death effects, energy drain, and any negative energy effects (such as from {i}inflict{/i} spells or {i}chill touch{/i}).\n\nThis spell doesn&#146;t remove negative levels that the subject has already gained, nor does it affect the saving throw necessary 24 hours after gaining a negative level.\n\n{i}Death ward{/i} does not protect against other sorts of attacks, such as hit point loss, poison, or petrification, even if those attacks might be lethal." compset="Spell" summary="Grants immunity to death spells and negative energy effects.">
