    </thing>
  <thing id="wBladeRetr" name="Blade, Retractable" description="A retractable blade is a simple weapon. You can release the blade as a free action. Pressing the blade back into its hilt is a move action that provokes attacks of opportunity. To notice the blade while it is retracted, an observer must make a successful Search check (DC 20). The DC drops to 15 if the observer physically examines the object." compset="Weapon">
