  <thing id="wCrsStake" name="Crossbow, Staking" description="A staking crossbow is an exotic weapon. Like a heavy crossbow, a staking crossbow requires two hands to use effectively, regardless of the user&apos;s size. Loading a staking crossbow is a full-round action that provokes attacks of opportunity.\n\nA Large or larger character can shoot, but now load, a staking crossbow with one hand at a -4 penalty. A Large or larger character can shoot a staking crossbow with each hand at a -6 penalty, plus the usual -4 penalty for the off-hand attack  (-6 primary/-10 offhand)." compset="Weapon">
