  <thing id="sBrdRheuma" name="Rheumatism" description="This spell sends a bolt of energy from the caster&apos;s hand to strike an enemy and fuse his bones into arthritic mounds, making it almost impossible to move or bend the afflicted limb.  The precise effect depends on where the bones are fused.  Under normal circumstances the ray strikes a random joint.  On a critical hit, however, you can decide precisely where the bolt strikes.\n\n{align left}\nd%       Location        \n01-05    Foot            Dex -2\n06-20    Knee            Dex -4. Speed reduced by one quarter. -4 competence penalty to attack.\n21-40    Pelvis/Back     Dex -6. Speed halved. -8 competence penalty to attack.\n4|-50    Hand/Wrist      Cannot grip (or release) held objects or use arm to cast spells with a somatic component. -2 competence penalty to attack.\n51-65    Elbow           Cannot use arm to cast spells with a somatic component. -4 competence penalty to attack.\n66-85    Shoulder        Cannot use arm to cast spells with a somatic component. -6 competence penalty to attack.\n86-00    Neck/Head       Cannot speak. turn head or cast spells with a verbal component. &#151;2 competence penalty to attack.\n\nCreatures without a skeleton (such as plants, oozes, and many aberrations and constructs) are immune to this spell.\nUndead who are normally immune to fortitude saves, are not nessisarily immune to this spell, at the determination of the GM.\n{b}Arcane Focus:{/b} A set of knucklebones from an animal that died of old age." compset="Spell">
