  <thing id="ioRLRelSta" name="Reliquary of Starvation" description="ln the domain of G&#146;Henna, this item is a highly prized honor granted to certain faithful by the Church of Zhakata.  {i}A reliquaijy of starvation{/i} is a box of red and black lacquered wood trimmed in human bones. The finger bones of a person who starved to death in devotion to Zhakata rest in the silk and velvet lined interior.  According to the priests of that vile god, as long as the person who owns the {i}reliquary of starvation{/i} prays at least twice per day to Zhakata, the reliquary will prevent him from dying of starvation.\n\nThis item prevents the bearer from accumulating more than half of her total hit points in subdual damage due to the effects of starvation. The bearer must pray to Zhakata for at least a total one hour per day to receive the reliquary&apos;s effects.\n\nCrafting a reliquary of starvation requires a powers check.\n{i}Caster Level{/i}: 12th; {i}Prerequisites{/i}: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}heroes&#146; feast{/i}, finger bones of a person who starved to death for Zhakata; {i}Market Price{/i}: 10,900 gp; {i}Weight{/i}: 5 lb." compset="Wondrous" stacking="never">
